      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEEP SPACE (4) shapes nicely here coming off an excellent 29.59 victory at Wentworth Park over 520m. In form and looks the one to beat again. CUMBRIA LAURA (1) missed the frame last time when fifth (30.16) at Wentworth Park but prior to that had four placings in a row. Form here sound including two wins. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Cannot be underestimated. TAP OUT RUSTY (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (30.37) in a Grade 5 at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. SPRING WITNESS (6) saluted at big odds last time, don't underestimate.",
